---
title: Glazed Peri Peri Chicken Thighs with Herby Chips and Zesty Green Beans & Peas
description: These Glazed Peri Peri Chicken Thighs are a crowd pleaser and are one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R01_W30_UK_F14628-5_Main__5low-ebf479aa.jpg
